title: Transfer goes wrong
body: So guys i lost 2600 rp to transfer my account to NA,while i wanted it to EUNE,riot please give me a chance and with that rp i lost move me to EUNE please

replies.body: So it looks like you accidentally picked to transfer your account to NA when you meant for it to be sent over to the EUNE servers? Reach out to our account team in a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and they should be able to get that fixed up for you!
